while they were shopping
for her wedding dress.

256
00:10:45,385 --> 00:10:46,715
So, there's that.

257
00:10:48,075 --> 00:10:49,919
I'm gonna go add
some more place settings,

258
00:10:50,381 --> 00:10:52,384
since there's
so many more of us.

259
00:10:53,247 --> 00:10:54,950
You know what,
I should... I should help.

260
00:10:55,038 --> 00:10:56,072
I'll... I'll be
