00:11:53,768 --> 00:11:55,341
And now I want
a sandwich.

284
00:11:55,803 --> 00:11:57,056
Saul-y.

285
00:11:57,143 --> 00:11:58,886
I'm so sorry,
Aunt Gertie.

286
00:11:58,973 --> 00:12:01,143
I... Hey.

287
00:12:16,783 --> 00:12:19,170
You look good, my boy.
Really good.

288
00:12:20,850 --> 00:12:23,373
I'm sorry you have to
see him this way.

289
00:12:23,461 --> 00:12:27,084
Gertie,
this is my f-friend Nico.

290
00:12:27,172 --> 00:12:28,172
Hi.

291
00:12:31,410 --> 00:12:33,217
W-Why aren't they
taking his body?

292
00:12:33,995 --> 00:12:35,818
Apparently, it's been
a big day here,

293
00:12:35,936 --> 00:12:37,944
so I've been watching him.

294
00:12:38,208 --> 00:12:40,031
But I understand that you'll
want to take over, so...

295
00:12:40,118 --> 00:12:41,118
Uh, I can't do that.

296
00:12:41,290 --> 00:12:42,943
Saul-y and I promised

297
00:12:44,037 --> 00:12:46,936
that when the end
was the end,

298
00:12:47,566 --> 00:12:49,309
that was the end.

299
00:12:49,967 --> 00:12:51,303
The end of...?

300
00:12:56,334 --> 00:12:57,506
Hmm.

301
00:12:57,763 --> 00:12:59,346
He was a good man.

302
00:13:02,864 --> 00:13:04,657
Love you, buddy.

303
00:13:06,475 --> 00:13:10,420
And you are a good man, too,
