wiring in like a decade.

415
00:17:25,395 --> 00:17:27,688
Sadly, we see it all the time
in old restaurants.

416
00:17:28,158 --> 00:17:29,807
That's a terrible story.

417
00:17:33,356 --> 00:17:36,231
Richard, you're a surgeon,
too, right? A general?

418
00:17:36,319 --> 00:17:37,705
Yes, I am.
At Pac-North.

419
00:17:37,847 --> 00:17:38,941
When I was in training,

420
00:17:39,029 --> 00:17:40,238
