just Pac-North,

432
00:18:06,576 --> 00:18:07,819
so you know.

433
00:18:08,053 --> 00:18:09,244
Not really a nickname.

434
00:18:09,332 --> 00:18:10,495
Actually,
it is a nickname.

435
00:18:10,583 --> 00:18:11,956
It's short for
Pacific Northwest.

436
00:18:12,044 --> 00:18:13,064
You say "actually"
a lot.

437
00:18:13,152 --> 00:18:15,355
I just meant that first
responders all over the city

438
00:18:15,443 --> 00:18:16,828
are talking about
the improvements

439
00:18:16,916 --> 00:18:17,893
over the past few months.

440
00:18:17,981 --> 00:18:19,745
