their patients there now.

441
00:18:19,832 --> 00:18:21,627
Oh, how about that?
That's really, really great.

442
00:18:21,714 --> 00:18:24,297
You mean they prefer to
go there over Grey-Sloan?

443
00:18:24,393 --> 00:18:26,056
- Mom.
- Catherine, you've only seen

