00:18:28,933 --> 00:18:30,518
The outside of your office.

447
00:18:30,606 --> 00:18:33,149
Hmm.
When?

448
00:18:33,237 --> 00:18:36,527
You were busy having coffee
with a friend.

449
00:18:38,620 --> 00:18:40,361
Just to clarify,
I like both hospitals.

450
00:18:40,449 --> 00:18:42,406
How about we just change
the subject entirely?

451
00:18:42,494 --> 00:18:43,367
- Yeah!
- I'm for that.

452
00:18:43,455 --> 00:18:44,716
- Please.
- Yay.

453
00:18:47,740 --> 00:18:50,073
It is your anniversary, 
right?

454
00:18:50,723 --> 00:18:52,127
How did you two meet?

455
00:19:02,889 --> 00:19:04,455
- Maybe we can just...
