was his wife.

479
00:20:32,357 --> 00:20:35,230
Gertie and Saul took each other
for who they were.

480
00:20:35,481 --> 00:20:40,283
They lived their lives,
never asked any questions,

481
00:20:40,838 --> 00:20:42,668
and they never told a soul.

482
00:20:45,513 --> 00:20:47,088
So you're...

