00:21:28,932 --> 00:21:32,588
Um, so, Catherine
hired a string quartet,

497
00:21:32,675 --> 00:21:35,289
and she's got them hiding
in the lobby of the hospital,

498
00:21:35,377 --> 00:21:38,484
which is filled with...
with roses and candles.

