00:21:47,713 --> 00:21:49,172
So, Richard's at work,

503
00:21:49,260 --> 00:21:51,281
and Catherine
starts shouting at him.

504
00:21:51,369 --> 00:21:52,638
And she's yelling about

505
00:21:52,725 --> 00:21:54,953
how Richard is worth
every heartbreak,

506
00:21:55,041 --> 00:21:57,555
and she doesn't care
if she looks like a fool

507
00:21:57,643 --> 00:22:00,083
